WEBVTT

00:00.090 --> 00:04.300
I put an electrical generator in Dad’s chest so he can start supporting himself.

00:04.720 --> 00:08.720
I’ve placed motors in him so he can start moving around little by little.

00:08.900 --> 00:13.080
The electricity heats him up, so he’s warm and gentle, just like my real Dad.

00:13.640 --> 00:17.520
I was feeling tired, so I gave him a hug.

00:17.680 --> 00:19.630
I held onto him like a little baby.
